581
00:35:25,970 --> 00:35:26,770
Tak perlulah.

582
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:29,320
Saya biasanya tak suka pakai barang kemas.

583
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,030
Mari makan.

584
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,590
Puteri,

585
00:35:36,740 --> 00:35:37,930
ini ikan Sungai Hong,

586
00:35:37,930 --> 00:35:38,850
