587
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:43,740
Puteri tak suka ikan ini juga?

588
00:35:43,750 --> 00:35:44,270
Saya...

589
00:35:44,690 --> 00:35:45,890
Saya tersangkut.

590
00:36:01,030 --> 00:36:03,320
Terkejut tak? Tak sangka, betul?

591
00:36:03,340 --> 00:36:04,820
Awak buat apa ini?

592
