604
00:36:34,850 --> 00:36:36,910
malah boleh bermalam dan ada tandas.

605
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,850
Semasa musim panas,

606
00:36:39,950 --> 00:36:40,950
peti ais kecil ini

607
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:43,280
boleh simpan minuman Poria
dan minuman mawar

608
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:45,630
untuk awak berehat, pulihkan tenaga
dan simpan tenaga

609
00:36:45,630 --> 00:36:46,690
dalam perjalanan.

610
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:47,660
Macam mana?

611
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,510
Agak bagus.

612
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:53,190
Putera Mahkota yang kacak dan menawan

613
00:36:53,190 --> 00:36:55,150
