622
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,070
Ya, Qiao.

623
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:09,000
Kenapa?

624
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:13,400
Berdasarkan pemahaman saya
terhadap Zhuge Yue,

625
