652
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,550
Jangan lupa tujuan kita ke sini,

653
00:38:07,550 --> 00:38:09,750
kita bukan datang untuk bersiar-siar.

654
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:10,950
Tak tahanlah.

655
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:12,000
Zhuge...

656
00:38:13,110 --> 00:38:14,110
Maharaja Ximeng,

657
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,920
