667
00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:29,800
Ada…

668
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,290
Tiga puluh buah.

669
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:34,670
Yang Amat Mulia,

670
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:35,860
