671
00:38:36,710 --> 00:38:38,230
Awak anggap ini 130 buah?

672
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:39,490
Bukankah ini 130 buah?

673
00:38:40,370 --> 00:38:40,890
Saya…

674
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:43,960
Seratus tiga puluh buah.

675
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:46,220
Mari kita pergi tengok yang seterusnya.

676
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:09,280
Penonton dah tiba,
pertunjukan akan bermula.

677
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,030
Xing Er,

678
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:12,400
