679
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:14,000
saya juga patut beri awak penjelasan.

680
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:15,330
Entah kenapa

681
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,450
perasaan saya terhadap dia

682
00:39:17,730 --> 00:39:19,380
buat saya begitu menderita.

683
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,550
Maksud awak,

684
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:27,150
jahitan ini mungkin sejenis kod rahsia?

685
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,400
Saya ajak awak ke sini

686
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,800
